{"tha-ap312:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap312:0.2":"Padumakesaravagga ","tha-ap312:0.3":"Pabbharadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap312:1.1":"“Piyadassino bhagavato, ","tha-ap312:1.2":"pabbharo sodhito maya; ","tha-ap312:1.3":"Ghatakanca upatthasim, ","tha-ap312:1.4":"paribhogaya tadino. ","tha-ap312:2.1":"Tam me buddho viyakasi, ","tha-ap312:2.2":"piyadassi mahamuni; ","tha-ap312:2.3":"Sahassakando satabhendu, ","tha-ap312:2.4":"dhajalu haritamayo. ","tha-ap312:3.1":"Nibbattissati so yupo, ","tha-ap312:3.2":"ratananca anappakam; ","tha-ap312:3.3":"Pabbharadanam datvana, ","tha-ap312:3.4":"kappam saggamhi modaham. ","tha-ap312:4.1":"Ito battimsakappamhi, ","tha-ap312:4.2":"susuddho nama khattiyo; ","tha-ap312:4.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap312:4.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap312:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap312:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap312:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap312:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma pabbharadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap312:7.1":"Pabbharadayakattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap312:8.1":"Padumakesaravaggo ekatimsatimo. ","tha-ap312:9.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap312:10.1":"Kesaram gandhamannanca, ","tha-ap312:10.2":"dhammasanni phalena ca; ","tha-ap312:10.3":"Pasadaramadayi ca, ","tha-ap312:10.4":"lepako buddhasannako; ","tha-ap312:10.5":"Pabbharado ca gathayo, ","tha-ap312:10.6":"ekapannasa kittita. "}